topic.title: JetBrains ReSharper Ultimate 2017.1.2 + Crack
topic.body:
Visual Studio 2017 support.

The ReSharper installer is identical to the one from the JetBrains website.

The crack installs a local license server, which is used to activate ReSharper. To be save, install the license server in a VM. The crack is not from me and I can not guarantee it's 100% malware free.
